{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket.send()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>binaryType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>bufferedAmount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>extensions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><em><code>send()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;<strong><code>WebSocket.send()</code></strong>&nbsp;方法将需要通过 WebSocket 链接传输至服务器的数据排入队列，并根据所需要传输的 data bytes 的大小来增加&nbsp;<code>bufferedAmount</code>的值&nbsp;。若数据无法传输（例如数据需要缓存而缓冲区已满）时，套接字会自行关闭。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">WebSocket.send(\"Hello server!\");</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"data\"><code>data</code></dt>\n <dd>用于传输至服务器的数据。它必须是以下类型之一：\n <dl>\n  <dt id=\"usvstring\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>文本字符串。字符串将以 UTF-8 格式添加到缓冲区，并且&nbsp;<code>bufferedAmount</code>&nbsp;将加上该字符串以 UTF-8 格式编码时的字节数的值。</dd>\n  <dt id=\"arraybuffer\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>您可以使用一有类型的数组对象发送底层二进制数据；其二进制数据内存将被缓存于缓冲区，<code>bufferedAmount</code>&nbsp;将加上所需字节数的值。</dd>\n  <dt id=\"blob\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></dt>\n  <dd><code>Blob</code>&nbsp;类型将队列 blob 中的原始数据以二进制中传输。&nbsp;<code>bufferedAmount</code>&nbsp;将加上原始数据的字节数的值。</dd>\n  <dt id=\"arraybufferview\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>ArrayBufferView</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>您可以以二进制帧的形式发送任何&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Typed_arrays\">JavaScript 类数组对象</a> ；其二进制数据内容将被队列于缓冲区中。值&nbsp;<code>bufferedAmount</code> 将加上必要字节数的值。</dd>\n </dl>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"invalid_state_err\"><code>INVALID_STATE_ERR</code></dt>\n <dd>当前连接未处于&nbsp;<code>OPEN</code>&nbsp;状态。</dd>\n <dt id=\"syntax_err\"><code>SYNTAX_ERR</code></dt>\n <dd>数据是一个包含未配对代理 (unpaired surrogates) 的字符串。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Gecko 在<span title=\"(Firefox 6.0 / Thunderbird 6.0 / SeaMonkey 2.3)\">Gecko&nbsp;6.0</span>中对&nbsp;<code>send()</code>&nbsp;方法的实现与规范有些不一致；&nbsp;Gecko 返回一个<code>boolean</code>&nbsp;来告知当前连接是否依旧处于<code>OPEN&nbsp;</code>状态&nbsp;(同时也可以使用该返回值来判定数据是否已经被完全缓存或者传输); 这个问题在 <span title=\"(Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5)\">Gecko&nbsp;8.0</span>中被修正。</p>\n\n<p>而 <span title=\"(Firefox 11.0 / Thunderbird 11.0 / SeaMonkey 2.8)\">Gecko&nbsp;11.0</span>, 支持&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a> 类型但不支持&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>类型。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-sockets.html#dom-websocket-send-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.WebSocket.send"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket.send","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"WebSocket.send() 方法将需要通过 WebSocket 链接传输至服务器的数据排入队列，并根据所需要传输的 data bytes 的大小来增加 bufferedAmount的值 。若数据无法传输（例如数据需要缓存而缓冲区已满）时，套接字会自行关闭。","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSocket.send()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSocket.send()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSocket.send()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/websocket/send","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/websocket/send/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket","title":"WebSocket"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send","title":"WebSocket.send()"}],"pageTitle":"WebSocket.send() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}